    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get the multi-factor thing, but doesn't it feel like certain policies specifically target the incentive to work? like, if the government is basically paying people to stay home, isn't that effectively a policy that discourages employment? it seems like a pretty clear-cut case of why we're seeing lower participation in some areas.",
